  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever since the anniversary of a young woman's death strange things have been happening at the White Oak Inn. Now, her spirit's roaming around, and an employee is receiving threatening letters. What dark secrets wait to be found? The clock is ticking and you, as Alex Hill, must uncover the truth before it’s too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Solve puzzles and interrogate suspects </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Find clues as you uncover the secrets of the White Oak Inn</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Enjoy a classic point-and-click adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Fully voice acted</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/7cacb1a6a1fb1711bec84f10ebd9d31a.poster.avif?t=1743693980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/7cacb1a6a1fb1711bec84f10ebd9d31a.webm?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/7cacb1a6a1fb1711bec84f10ebd9d31a.mp4?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Follow Alex in her story as she cracks the case!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/6ddd6fbde99377633a186ff77b3d5651.poster.avif?t=1743693980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/6ddd6fbde99377633a186ff77b3d5651.webm?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/6ddd6fbde99377633a186ff77b3d5651.mp4?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Solve puzzles and find clues in a haunted inn.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/02102f2aef681f5448daed7cea83d166.poster.avif?t=1743693980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/02102f2aef681f5448daed7cea83d166.webm?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/02102f2aef681f5448daed7cea83d166.mp4?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Interact with interesting characters as you discover whodunnit.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever since the anniversary of a young woman's death strange things have been happening at the White Oak Inn. Now, her spirit's roaming around, and an employee is receiving threatening letters. What dark secrets wait to be found? The clock is ticking and you, as Alex Hill, must uncover the truth before it’s too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Solve puzzles and interrogate suspects </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Find clues as you uncover the secrets of the White Oak Inn</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Enjoy a classic point-and-click adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◘  Fully voice acted</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/7cacb1a6a1fb1711bec84f10ebd9d31a.poster.avif?t=1743693980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/7cacb1a6a1fb1711bec84f10ebd9d31a.webm?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/7cacb1a6a1fb1711bec84f10ebd9d31a.mp4?t=1743693980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Follow Alex in her story as she cracks the case!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/6ddd6fbde99377633a186ff77b3d5651.poster.avif?t=1743693980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2859200/extras/6ddd6fbde99377633a186ff77b3d5651.webm?